"The user begins with View 1 (overview) to compare seasonal yield variations across districts. Clicking a district in the bar chart filters Views 2 and 3 to focus on that region. In View 2, the scatter plot reveals land-use efficiency patterns, while View 3's heatmap provides crop recommendations based on historical yields for the selected district. The season toggle in View 3 allows comparisons between Kharif and Rabi performance."